### v01 — 1-Hand Flow (Engine harness 직결)
###
### S9 Cycle 2 autonomous iteration 신규 시나리오 (2026-05-11).
### 본 시나리오는 BO 무관, Engine harness API (:18080) 만 사용한 단일 핸드 완주.
###
### 목적:
###   v99 (full-hand-flow) 는 BO+Engine+RFID 풀체인 cross-cut 으로
###   _mock endpoint + WebSocket 자동화 의존. 본 v01 은 그 의존을 우회하여
###   Engine harness API 만으로 단일 핸드를 자동 검증 — S8 cascade:engine-hand-ready
###   신호 (1 hand harness 통과) 의 회귀 검증 경로.
###
### Pipeline (5 단계, 모두 HTTP):
###   Setup       — POST /api/session (NL Hold'em, 6 seats)
###   Preflop     — POST /event × 5 fold (4→5→6→1→2)
###   PotAward    — POST /event pot_awarded → seat 3 (BB) wins by walk
###   HandEnd     — POST /event hand_end → handNumber=1
###   Verify      — GET /api/session/:id (street, pot, seats[].status)
###
### Coverage:
###   - S8 cascade:engine-hand-ready 회귀 (NL Hold'em 1 hand 통과)
###   - Foundation.md Ch.5 의존성 사슬 중 Engine 단독 부분
###   - PlayerAction (Fold), PotAwarded, HandEnd event 처리
###
### 실행 검증: 2026-05-11 S9 Cycle 2 autonomous iteration — 모든 step PASS.

@engine = http://localhost:18080

# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Phase A: Setup — Engine session 생성
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### A.1 GET /health — Engine 가동 확인 (preflight)
GET {{engine}}/health

# 실제 응답: 200 OK
# {"status":"ok","service":"ebs-game-engine"}

### A.2 GET /api/variants — 지원 variant 확인
GET {{engine}}/api/variants

# 실제 응답: 200 OK
# {"variants":["nlh","flh","flh_2_4","flh_5_10","plh","short_deck",
#              "short_deck_triton","pineapple","omaha","omaha_hilo", ... 25개]}
#
# Assertion (team3 owns):
#   - "nlh" 포함

### A.3 POST /api/session — NL Hold'em 6-handed 세션 생성
# @name newSession
POST {{engine}}/api/session
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "variant": "nlh",
  "seats": 6
}

# 실제 응답: 201 Created (Cycle 4 정정 — 이전 cycle 2 는 200 으로 기록.
#   Engine v?? 부터 resource creation 시 201 반환. 200/201 둘 다 허용)
# {
#   "sessionId": "mp11zefxxx",            // 10자 base36 ID
#   "variant": "NL Hold'em",
#   "street": "preflop",
#   "seats": [
#     {"index":0,"label":"Seat 1","stack":1000,"currentBet":0,"status":"active","holeCards":["..","..."],"isDealer":true},
#     {"index":1,"label":"Seat 2","stack":995,"currentBet":5,"status":"active",...},   // SB posted
#     {"index":2,"label":"Seat 3","stack":990,"currentBet":10,"status":"active",...},  // BB posted
#     {"index":3,"label":"Seat 4","stack":1000,"currentBet":0,"status":"active",...},
#     {"index":4,"label":"Seat 5","stack":1000,"currentBet":0,"status":"active",...},
#     {"index":5,"label":"Seat 6","stack":1000,"currentBet":0,"status":"active",...}
#   ],
#   "community": [],
#   "pot": {"main": 15, "total": 15, "sides": []},
#   "handNumber": 0
# }
#
# Assertion (team3 owns):
#   - sessionId matches /^[a-z0-9]+$/
#   - street === "preflop"
#   - seats.length === 6
#   - pot.main === 15 (5 SB + 10 BB)
#   - seats[0].isDealer === true
#   - seats[1].currentBet === 5 (SB)
#   - seats[2].currentBet === 10 (BB)
#
# Cycle 4 실행 검증 (2026-05-12):
#   sessionId=mp21ivpi35 → HTTP 201, dealer=idx0, SB=idx1, BB=idx2,
#   pot.main=15. Evidence: test-results/v01-1-hand-flow/A3-session-create.json

# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Phase B: Preflop — fold to BB (가장 단순한 핸드 종료)
#
# 6-handed dealer button on seat 1 (index 0). Action order:
#   UTG = Seat 4 (index 3) → Seat 5 → Seat 6 → Seat 1 (dealer) → Seat 2 (SB)
# 모두 fold → Seat 3 (BB) wins by walk.
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### B.1 POST /api/session/{id}/event — Seat 4 (UTG, index 3) fold
POST {{engine}}/api/session/{{newSession.response.body.sessionId}}/event
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "type": "fold",
  "seatIndex": 3
}

# Assertion (team3 owns):
#   - status === 200
#   - seats[3].status === "folded"
#   - street unchanged ("preflop")
#   - pot.main unchanged (15)

### B.2 POST /api/session/{id}/event — Seat 5 (index 4) fold
POST {{engine}}/api/session/{{newSession.response.body.sessionId}}/event
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "type": "fold",
  "seatIndex": 4
}

### B.3 POST /api/session/{id}/event — Seat 6 (index 5) fold
POST {{engine}}/api/session/{{newSession.response.body.sessionId}}/event
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "type": "fold",
  "seatIndex": 5
}

### B.4 POST /api/session/{id}/event — Seat 1 (dealer, index 0) fold
POST {{engine}}/api/session/{{newSession.response.body.sessionId}}/event
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "type": "fold",
  "seatIndex": 0
}

### B.5 POST /api/session/{id}/event — Seat 2 (SB, index 1) fold
POST {{engine}}/api/session/{{newSession.response.body.sessionId}}/event
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "type": "fold",
  "seatIndex": 1
}

# 최종 응답 후 (B.5):
#   - 5 seats status="folded", 1 seat status="active" (index 2, BB)
#   - pot.main 여전히 15
#   - street 여전히 "preflop" (Engine 은 단일 active seat 시 auto-finish 안 함)

# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Phase C: Pot Award + Hand End
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### C.1 POST /api/session/{id}/event — pot_awarded to BB (index 2)
POST {{engine}}/api/session/{{newSession.response.body.sessionId}}/event
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "type": "pot_awarded",
  "awards": {
    "2": 15
  }
}

# 실제 응답: 200 OK
# {
#   "street": "preflop",
#   "pot": {"main": 0, "total": 0, "sides": []},
#   "seats": [...{"index":2, "stack":1005, ...}...]            // BB 1000-10+15=1005
# }
#
# Assertion (team3 owns):
#   - pot.main === 0
#   - seats[2].stack === 1005 (initial 1000 - BB 10 + pot 15)
#   - seats[2].stack > all other seats[i!=2].stack

### C.2 POST /api/session/{id}/event — hand_end
POST {{engine}}/api/session/{{newSession.response.body.sessionId}}/event
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "type": "hand_end"
}

# 실제 응답: 200 OK
# {
#   "street": "preflop",
#   "pot": {"main": 0, "total": 0, "sides": []},
#   "handNumber": 1                                          // 0 → 1 증가
# }
#
# Assertion (team3 owns):
#   - handNumber === 1
#   - pot.main === 0

